display_long_description:
# Crush the Hordes with Colossal Mechs

In a ruined world, power is survival! Experience overwhelming scale and destructive power like never before Pilot your giant mech and wipe the zombies off the face of the earth
[media]

# The Unknown Beyond the Dunes

Vast deserts. Boiling lava. Acid-corroded machinery. Factories and towns.

Prepare to explore a world of infinite mystery beyond the chaos
[media]


# Unpredictable Undead Threats

Zombies rush blindly and strike from the air without warning. Drop your guard for a second, and it’s game over.
[media]

# Seize Greater Power

Customize your BUST with special gears to match the ever-growing chaos. To survive this endless madness, you need absolute power.
[media]

# Zombies Aren't the Only Enemy

Face off against other chickens. Friend or foe? The choice is yours Just keep your weapons ready
[media]

# Style Is Confidence

Even in the apocalypse, looks matter Stand out with unique costumes and BUST decals
[media]

# More Fun News and Events on Discord!
👉 discord.gg/chickingdead
